Type: Package
Package: clc
Title: Tools for Working with CORINE Land Cover Data and Styles
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jose", "Samos", , "jsamos@ugr.es", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4457-3439")),
    person("Universidad de Granada", role = "cph")
  )
Description: clc provides functions to facilitate the management,
    analysis, and visualization of CORINE Land Cover data, addressing
    challenges related to its classification system and associated styles,
    including color mappings and descriptive labels.
